727777f-a.title: Queens: Queens Boulevard - 75th Avenue
727777f-a.text:
Oueens Boulevard (foreground, not seen), at the S. W. corner of
Seventy-fifth Avenue (formerly Atom Place), showing the home of David
Springsteen in a set of two views. It was still owned by the family
in 1924. The house was demolished in October 1928.
1922.
View 2: July 1923.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.
